Couple of shots from my gig with @mcbrainpower last week in Delft. Much love to all the peeps who came to party with us! 
Got to do my cuts, backings and played some tunes before and after the show and rocked with the CDJ's for this one. 
Make sure you're able to play on different devices, just in case your own kit isn't available. You know turntables are always my first choice, but I learned how to use the CDJ's as well so I'm always good to go. 
Same thing with mixers: you never know when you'll walk into a club to do a set and the don't have 'your' mixer. Do 't let that hold you back! 
I remember back in the days when most clubs here had the big Dateq mixers with the long faders and no crossfader. And the DJ sets were all built into the booth so you couldn't even connect your own mixer if you brought it to the club 😂😂😂 So you had no choice and you had to learn to work with whatever was available. I'm so glad I went through that because it made me a better DJ ✊🏾 #DJ #gigs #gig #brainpower #tlm #MC #hiphop #turntablism #show #perform #scratch #crowd #hype #hits #delft
